  <brief_title>Fabry and Stroke Epidemiological Protocol (FASEP): Risk Factors In Ischemic Stroke Patients With Fabry Disease</brief_title>
  <acronym>FASEP</acronym>
  <official_title>FASEP Fabry and Stroke Epidemiological Protocol RISK FACTORS IN ISCHEMIC STROKE PATIENTS WITH FABRY DISEASE AN INTERNATIONAL, MULTICENTER, EPIDEMIOLOGICAL PROTOCOL</official_title>
